name: Ophiuchus
description: Vigilant and calm, you are on your guard for many reasons. In this dangerous and unequal world, you don't trust anybody. You want to be protected against the contagion phenomena. People are crazy and ready to kill each other for their essential needs. Ophiuchus is a unique anti-bacterial ensemble that will give you ultimate protection against all external viruses. Its finesse facilitates acrobatic movements when it's time for you to defend yourself.
